dmca.title: Images DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.sender_name: Copyright Information and Anti-piracy Centre Finland

works.description:
The copyrighted work at issue is  
the "Jäsenet paikalleen, paha veri pois" by Antti Hernesniemi, published
by  
Yliopistopaino, ISBN #9515702240.

The whole book has been scanned and uploaded as 68 separate pictures as a 

single Picasaweb album without authorization from the right holder.
